{
  "texts": [
    "MIWAE combines probabilistic a approache with deep-learning scalability.",
    "It is theoretically sound under MAR, easy to train, and produces both point and multiple imputations that capture uncertainty.",
    "[45] extends conditional score-based diffusion models to tabular data with mixed numerical and categorical features.",
    "The method learns to generate plausible values for the missing part x mis i conditioned on the observed part x obs i through a self-supervised denoising objective.",
    "During training, some features are randomly masked and reconstructed from noisy versions, while observed values remain fixed to provide context."
  ]
}